snippet.title: Smash Puck - Trailer
snippet.description: Smash Puck is the game you get when you combine pool, pinball, air hockey, minigolf, curling and add magnets, portals, moving platforms, force fields and more! Now available on the App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/smash-puck/id1386816439
